---
title: Tahini & Honey-Glazed Chicken with Zesty Garlic Rice & Cucumber Salsa
description: Tahini might just be the hardest working little seed spread we know. Tonight, it’s lending its unique talents to an amazing homemade glaze that transforms any weeknight supper into a glorious production.

*Unfortunately, this week's tomato was in short supply, so we've replaced it with baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ef2ed1a2af9653ee91b1ece-99ec5547.jpg
